---

<section id="about" class="py-20 px-4 relative">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="ascii-box inline-block mb-4">
        <span class="text-amber-500">$</span> cat about.md
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Über mich</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <!-- Text content -->
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Hey, ich bin David — <span class="text-amber-500 font-semibold">Full-Stack Developer</span> mit Fokus auf TypeScript, React und Laravel.
          Ich baue seit über 5 Jahren Web-Applikationen — vom MVP bis zur produktionsreifen Architektur.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Neben der Entwicklung bin ich <span class="text-emerald-400 font-semibold">Dozent bei der DBE-Academy</span>, 
          wo ich zeigen kann, wie man wirklich gute Web-Software baut. Grundlagen, Architektur, Best Practices — 
          mit ordentlich Praxisbezug und ohne langweilige Slides 🍻
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Zurzeit beschäftige ich mich intensiv mit AI/MLOps — besonders mit Agentic AI, RAG-Architekturen 
          und der Frage, wie man LLMs sinnvoll in bestehende Systeme einbaut. Bleibt also spannend.
        </p>

        <!-- GitHub Stats - Removed external shields.io images to reduce blocking requests -->
        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 pt-6 mt-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500 font-mono mb-4">// GitHub Stats</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <a href="https://github.com/davidschuchert" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl hover:bg-amber-50 dark:hover:bg-amber-900/20 transition-colors">
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Followers</span>
              <span class="font-mono font-bold text-amber-500">-</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/DavidSchuchert?tab=repositories" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl hover:bg-amber-50 dark:hover:bg-amber-900/20 transition-colors">
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Stars</span>
              <span class="font-mono font-bold text-amber-500">-</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/DavidSchuchert" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl hover:bg-amber-50 dark:hover:bg-amber-900/20 transition-colors">
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Languages</span>
              <span class="font-mono font-bold text-amber-500">-</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Fun facts -->
        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 pt-6 mt-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500 font-mono mb-3">// Status: Gaming-Setup aktiviert 🎮</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-amber-500">🍻</span> Bad Hersfeld, Germany
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-emerald-400">⚡</span> TypeScript Enthusiast
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-amber-500">📚</span> AI / MLOps Learner
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ASCII Art Character Card -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="ascii-box p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-100 to-gray-50 dark:from-gray-900 dark:to-gray-950 border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-900">
          <pre class="text-sm leading-tight text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-mono">
    ╔══════════════════════════╗
    ║  <span class="text-amber-500">David Schuchert</span>       ║
    ╠══════════════════════════╣
    ║  🎮 Gaming-Opa          ║
    ║  💻 Full-Stack Dev      ║
    ║  🎓 DBE-Academy Dozent ║
    ║  🤖 AI/MLOps Explorer  ║
    ║                          ║
    ║  [##########] 100%       ║
    ║  Passion enabled         ║
    ╚══════════════════════════╝
